    <p>Global #SprintWeekend will be 17-18 January 2015.</p>
<p>Please encourage contributors you know to host a small local sprint near them.</p>
<p>Post an announcement in your local meetup groups please; ask if anyone is interested in hosting a sprint and wants some support organizing it.</p>
<p>List sprints on the wiki: <a href="https://groups.drupal.org/node/447258" title="https://groups.drupal.org/node/447258">https://groups.drupal.org/node/447258</a><br />
That wiki also has more information about organizing a sprint.</p>
<p>We will have a couple meetings to support organizers (doodle for organizer support meetings: <a href="http://doodle.com/uutcp2ge7gt3a8ed" title="http://doodle.com/uutcp2ge7gt3a8ed">http://doodle.com/uutcp2ge7gt3a8ed</a> )<br />
and also have mentors in irc over the sprint days (doodle for mentoring during the sprint: <a href="http://doodle.com/5vr54mpvxq4k7x29" title="http://doodle.com/5vr54mpvxq4k7x29">http://doodle.com/5vr54mpvxq4k7x29</a> ).</p>
